c: 11
v: 61
t: "Uye kumaThamood takatumira mukoma wavo Swaalih. Akati: “Imi vanhu vangu! Namatai Allah: hamuna umwe mwari kunze kwavo. Vakakusikai kubva munyika uye vakakugarisai mairi, nokudaro kumbirai ruregerero kwavari uye modzoka kwavari. Zvirokwazvo, Tenzi vangu vari pedyo (neruzivo rwavo), vanopindura.”"